reviewText: It is the best movie I have ever seen.

I unfortunately did not read the reviews before I bought this. What a waste of money and disappointment. DVD did not work in my DVD player hopefully others are smart enough to read the reviews first. I will be steering clear from this seller and will be more careful on Amazon.

We bought this movie for our grandson. It CAN NOT be watched because they are selling d.v.d.'s that say "can not be watched in this region" WHAT kind of nonsense is this. You need to live in the U.K. To watch it. VERY disappointed to say the least.
When I purchased the movie it wasn't clear that this couldn't be viewed on US DVD players. Can't watch it and the company won't accept returns. Biggest disappointment EVER!
This DVD does not fit into a DVD Player... Not sure what this Disc is for.... Tried to put it into the LapTop Computer & it's stuck inside the Computer... What a total waste...
The DVD would not work because it said Wrong Region
The DVD I received would not work in my DVD player (although my other DVDs work fine).  I was very unhappy that I didn't get to see this movie.
I made a mistake in ordering this as a prime video.  I want to cancel this.  I did order The Return of the Jedi on DVD.  Sorry for the mistake.  Please cancel the prime video.
A classic, and the bonus features are pretty cool.
Bought the movie for Amazon Video (not the DVD) and it works great for me.
Fantastic movietime escape to my childhood.

Star wars return of the Jedi is one of my favorite films in the star wars films and yes this is a region 2 DVD which means you can't watch it in the us unless you have a multi region DVD player which i have
